---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 384
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Steadfastness
By: Henry Madathanas
---
The active heat produces the colour black in what is wet： in what is
dry. the colour white： and in what is white, the colour yellow.

First comes mortification, then calcination, and finally the golden
tincture produced by the light of the sacred fire which illumines the
purified soul.
